des:
How to use Amesbury Dental:

To get started, say “Alexa, open Amesbury Dental”

After the Welcome Message, here are some of the questions you can ask

 Ex.) What are your hours? 
 Ex.) What is the address to Amesbury Dental?
 Ex.) Tell me about your services.
 Ex.) Tell me about teeth whitening

In the Amesbury Dental app,
 
You can search for more information on the following topics/services:

- Dental Implants
- Teeth Whitening
- Porcelain Veneers
- CEREC Crowns

Check back in regularly with the Amesbury Dental app to listen to learn about our services. We update our content regularly to keep you up-to-date with the latest news, services, and company information!
